\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
The sufficient statistics approach we just saw relies on 3 things
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
The reform being analyzed is small
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
There are no other distortions in the economy
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Decisions about the structure of the environment that pin down which elasticitie
s are sufficient in a particular setting
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
This paper:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Provide a general framework to showcase how general sufficient statistics
 approach is
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Show how it generalizes when we relax 1.
 and 2.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Show how quickly the estimation requirements go up!
